oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Croft family photograph in Cuba
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of a group of four women and two men posing for a photograph on a porch in Cuba. From left to right: an unidentified woman, Margaret Croft, Elise Croft, Kate Croft, William Croft, and an unidentified man. The women are wearing white dresses while the men are wearing dark colored suits. They are sitting on wicker furniture.
